---
title: Veggie & Bacon Flatbread Pizza Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinnertime? A DIY veggie pizza bar! Keep it simple with marinara and mozzarella, or, go all out with zucchini, sautéed pepper, and fresh tomato. Out of the oven, drizzle with ranch and/or balsamic glaze and serve with peppery arugula salad. Order chicken sausage and fresh burrata cheese for even more options!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/686e0def8d751c3919190e9b-cf3696ae.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/686e0def8d751c3919190e9b-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
